{"tid":60963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巨乳一定吃香？ 研究：男性最愛這種乳房","createTime":"2016-12-30T23:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T05:07:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0de194d6d056595806c602572e35ff81e9fbca77","tid":60963,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:10:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1932869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1932869&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0833ded3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1932869&h=ca1111b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1932869</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-30 17:01 <br />\n〔編譯陳正健／綜合報導〕一般認為，男性大多是巨乳控。不過，根據捷克的最新研究，男性最愛的女性胸部形狀，其實是堅挺勻稱的類型，而非容易下垂的大奶。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/dec/30/images/bigPic/400_400/1932869_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fdec%2F30%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2F1932869_1.jpg&h=a5a8d72e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n捷克最新研究顯示，男性最愛的女性胸部形狀，其實是堅挺勻稱的類型，而非容易下垂的大奶。（美聯社） <br />\n<br />\n布拉格查理大學 （Prague's Charles University）針對捷克、巴西、喀麥隆和納米比亞等4國的267名男性進行調查，要求他們觀看兩組不同尺寸和堅挺度的乳房照片。 <br />\n<br />\n研究發現，4國男性對乳房的偏好各有差異，但多數最愛中等大小的乳房，其次才是巨乳，最不青睞貧乳。共同點是，4國男性皆愛堅挺的乳形。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，研究也指出，男性更愛堅挺勻稱的乳房，而非最為宏偉、卻易下垂的巨乳，這有別與過去的迷思，亦即大胸部女性生育能力更強，更能激起男人的性慾。 <br />\n<br />\n研究作者哈里夫切克（Jan Havliček）指出，研究發現跨文化的一致性，男性皆偏愛堅挺的乳房，這是年輕女性的典型性徵。 <br />\n<br />\n本研究刊登於《演化與人類行為》（Evolution and Human Behavior）期刊。"},{"pid":"f653de0d7cb14f74204950345882371e41071264","tid":60963,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咪吃香囉"},{"pid":"360eae5d56353d081611e80258f44f634680aec0","tid":60963,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"唔除衫都唔會知堅唔堅挺"},{"pid":"11049d20b34999a29ba6befdb5f4e7c1e23b40cd","tid":60963,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:53:41.000Z","msg":"針對捷克、巴西、喀麥隆和納米比亞等4國的267名男性進行調查，要求他們觀看兩組不同尺寸和堅挺度的乳房照片<br />\n<br />\n並不代表本人立場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e45da31808423800da101177b417f621536f89","tid":60963,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"J Law <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913914390912627c34e0884a0aabf3f87c73a00a","tid":60963,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"你講啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我最鐘意大到dup落黎個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3429f26020329a8424c99aa64ad84d8f1d5cb4a","tid":60963,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:29:11.000Z","msg":"貧乳冇得堅挺"},{"pid":"5e18f530c088fe6157353069387a69c534b4cf3f","tid":60963,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:29:17.000Z","msg":"最不青睞貧乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港班平胸怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caca7b6979e8dccdb2a355b436b59d01c53bc7e","tid":60963,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:37:01.000Z","msg":"JLaw真係好正 好想屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5981d1084e6a0e8c5bd8d989e5cda8a9163b